{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-tsx","path":"/tagteach/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Ian Chu"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7d808c6e-f4c6-5c3c-9c60-255b457951d1","excerpt":"之前有介紹過如何在 tag manager 安裝 ga 追蹤碼，埋設 tag manager 的追蹤碼到網頁後，再來開始進入 tag manager 設定，首先點選 觸發 建立好觸發邏輯，再進入 代碼 增加 ga…","html":"<p>之前有介紹過如何在 tag manager 安裝 ga 追蹤碼，埋設 tag manager 的追蹤碼到網頁後，再來開始進入 tag manager 設定，首先點選 <em>觸發</em> 建立好觸發邏輯，再進入 <em>代碼</em> 增加 ga 追蹤碼，綁定設定好的觸發點，再點選提交上去，就完成設定了。</p>\n<p>雖然上次有順手寫掉事件設定，但沒有特別介紹每個設定的邏輯，這次會帶更多細節。以 <a href=\"https://work.ianccy.com/commentboard/\" title=\"留言板\">留言板</a> 為範例。</p>\n<p>假設我們要追蹤送出留言，建立一個事件，拿進 ga 當作轉換目標。</p>\n<p>文章連結：<a href=\"https://ianccy.com/tagmanager/\" title=\"tag manager 安裝追蹤碼\">tag manager 安裝追蹤碼</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"tag-manager-設定邏輯\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tag-manager-%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A%E9%82%8F%E8%BC%AF\" aria-label=\"tag manager 設定邏輯 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Tag manager 設定邏輯</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">設定 <span class=\"token function\">trigger</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">觸發</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> 設定 <span class=\"token function\">tag</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">代碼</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token function\">publish</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>提交<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> 每個步驟中都可以使用變數</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"查看-html-標籤\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B-html-%E6%A8%99%E7%B1%A4\" aria-label=\"查看 html 標籤 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>查看 html 標籤</h3>\n<p>所有的設定都會走上面的流程，每個代碼都一定要包含觸發。這邊我們先做一個觸發，時機點是在送出留言的時候。</p>\n<p>我們先打開連結 => <a href=\"https://work.ianccy.com/commentboard/\" title=\"留言板\">留言板</a>，打開 chrome devtool( 滑鼠右鍵 -> 檢查 )，點選上面的 Elements，點擊左上角的游標標誌。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1a80a94f5c69318ca8d49c6f374804ff/acfc1/tagchromedev.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 55.15151515151515%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/1a80a94f5c69318ca8d49c6f374804ff/a805d/tagchromedev.webp 495w,\n/static/1a80a94f5c69318ca8d49c6f374804ff/6ec60/tagchromedev.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/1a80a94f5c69318ca8d49c6f374804ff/b3db0/tagchromedev.png 495w,\n/static/1a80a94f5c69318ca8d49c6f374804ff/acfc1/tagchromedev.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/1a80a94f5c69318ca8d49c6f374804ff/acfc1/tagchromedev.png\"\n            alt=\"chrome devtool\"\n            title=\"chrome devtool\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">chrome devtool</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>再把游標移到網頁上，會發現出現選取整個區塊，這時候移動到送出按鈕，用游標點擊一下，會發現右邊的 html 會變成選取樣式。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c6decf8fb56f675036f3556579fc71b1/acfc1/tagchromedev2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.37373737373738%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/c6decf8fb56f675036f3556579fc71b1/a805d/tagchromedev2.webp 495w,\n/static/c6decf8fb56f675036f3556579fc71b1/6ec60/tagchromedev2.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/c6decf8fb56f675036f3556579fc71b1/b3db0/tagchromedev2.png 495w,\n/static/c6decf8fb56f675036f3556579fc71b1/acfc1/tagchromedev2.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/c6decf8fb56f675036f3556579fc71b1/acfc1/tagchromedev2.png\"\n            alt=\"chrome devtool2\"\n            title=\"chrome devtool2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">chrome devtool2</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h4 id=\"按鈕-html\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%8C%89%E9%88%95-html\" aria-label=\"按鈕 html permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>按鈕 HTML</h4>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>button type<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"button\"</span> id<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"submitComment\"</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"btn btn-secondary\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  送出\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>button<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>這時候會發現按鈕的 id <code class=\"language-text\">submitComment</code>，通常來說一個頁面的 id 只會存在一個，所以我們會用這個 id 被點擊來作為觸發點，如果你要用 className 也是沒問題，只要處理好判斷即可。</p>\n<p>學會查看網頁的 html 很重要，學會這個工具的話，對你在設定追蹤數據有很大幫助。</p>\n<h2 id=\"i觸發條件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#i%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"i觸發條件 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>I.觸發條件</h2>\n<p>先來開始 tag manager 第一個步驟，設定觸發條件。</p>\n<p>打開 tag manager 網頁 <a href=\"https://tagmanager.google.com\" title=\"tagmanager\">tagmanager</a>，點擊觸發條件 => 新增。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e57355aa266bdb5783aae45ec8645941/acfc1/tagtri.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.7979797979798%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/e57355aa266bdb5783aae45ec8645941/a805d/tagtri.webp 495w,\n/static/e57355aa266bdb5783aae45ec8645941/6ec60/tagtri.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/e57355aa266bdb5783aae45ec8645941/b3db0/tagtri.png 495w,\n/static/e57355aa266bdb5783aae45ec8645941/acfc1/tagtri.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/e57355aa266bdb5783aae45ec8645941/acfc1/tagtri.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager trigger\"\n            title=\"tag manager trigger\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager trigger</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>這時候點擊觸發條件設定，右邊會展開一大堆選項， 大概分類為 網頁瀏覽、點擊、使用者主動參與、其他，這四種。</p>\n<p>我們選擇點擊元素，依狀況不同設定進階條件。選擇要執行的網頁路徑、click id 填上 submitComment。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f804470e834ddf91710ad5d13024627c/acfc1/tagsmaple4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.5959595959596%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/f804470e834ddf91710ad5d13024627c/a805d/tagsmaple4.webp 495w,\n/static/f804470e834ddf91710ad5d13024627c/6ec60/tagsmaple4.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/f804470e834ddf91710ad5d13024627c/b3db0/tagsmaple4.png 495w,\n/static/f804470e834ddf91710ad5d13024627c/acfc1/tagsmaple4.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/f804470e834ddf91710ad5d13024627c/acfc1/tagsmaple4.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager tagsmaple4\"\n            title=\"tag manager tagsmaple4\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager tagsmaple4</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h3 id=\"tag-manager-觸發簡易介紹\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#tag-manager-%E8%A7%B8%E7%99%BC%E7%B0%A1%E6%98%93%E4%BB%8B%E7%B4%B9\" aria-label=\"tag manager 觸發簡易介紹 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>tag manager 觸發簡易介紹</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.google.com/tagmanager/topic/7679384?hl=zh-Hant&#x26;ref_topic=3441647\" title=\"tag manager 官方觸發條件介紹\">tag manager 官方觸發條件介紹</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"網頁瀏覽\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E7%B6%B2%E9%A0%81%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BD\" aria-label=\"網頁瀏覽 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>網頁瀏覽</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>網頁瀏覽\n使用者一進入網頁，就會觸發 網頁瀏覽。</li>\n<li>DOM 就緒\n當使用者進入網頁後，會開始讀取 DOM (html)內容，從上往下跑一次，跑到底就會觸發 DOM 就緒。</li>\n<li>視窗已載入\n當讀取完成 DOM 之後，會繼續執行載入檔案內容，例如圖片、影片、js css 檔案、iframe 等等，當這些都載入完成，就會觸發 視窗已載入。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"點擊\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E9%BB%9E%E6%93%8A\" aria-label=\"點擊 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>點擊</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>僅連結\n使用者點選連結 (<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;a href=\"domain/pathname\">Link Text&lt;/a></code>)，才會觸發。</li>\n<li>所有元素\n使用者隨意在頁面上做點擊動作，就會觸發。例如我點了網頁的空白區塊，就會觸發了。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"使用者主動參與\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80%85%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87\" aria-label=\"使用者主動參與 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>使用者主動參與</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>YouTube 影片\n當網站上嵌入 youtube 影片，觀看影片的各種狀況，開始、暫停、完成播放，觀看影片的百分比設定。</li>\n<li>元素可見度\n網頁上物件出現在畫面上，都可以算是觸發元素可見度。包括載入出現、滾動出現、變化樣式 css 等等。</li>\n<li>捲動頁數\n針對滾動整個網頁觸發，用來計算滾動的百分比，可以讓自己定義要追蹤的比率。</li>\n<li>表單提交\n使用者提交表單就會觸發，<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;form>&lt;button>送出&lt;/button>&lt;/form></code>form html 架構才會觸發，如果是使用 javascript ajax 傳輸，就不會觸發到表單提交。</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"其他\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96\" aria-label=\"其他 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>其他</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>JavaScript 錯誤\n使用 window.onError 來監聽錯誤，會提供錯誤訊息、錯誤網址、錯誤行號碼等資訊。</li>\n<li>自訂事件\ndataLayer.push({event:{eventName}})，會依照 dataLayer 中 event 觸發。</li>\n<li>計時器\n可以設定某個動作觸發開始計時，之後再依照設定的時間倒數後在觸發另一個事件。</li>\n<li>記錄變更\n當使用 history.pushState()時會被觸發，可以處理 spa 的網址變化，運用在 react-router。</li>\n</ul>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4eae0c236535523cf1571c5191a00458/acfc1/triggerlist.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 107.27272727272728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/4eae0c236535523cf1571c5191a00458/a805d/triggerlist.webp 495w,\n/static/4eae0c236535523cf1571c5191a00458/6ec60/triggerlist.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/4eae0c236535523cf1571c5191a00458/b3db0/triggerlist.png 495w,\n/static/4eae0c236535523cf1571c5191a00458/acfc1/triggerlist.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/4eae0c236535523cf1571c5191a00458/acfc1/triggerlist.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager triggerlist\"\n            title=\"tag manager triggerlist\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager triggerlist</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"ii變數\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ii%E8%AE%8A%E6%95%B8\" aria-label=\"ii變數 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>II.變數</h2>\n<p>變數可能會比較抽象，簡單介紹一下什麼叫做變數，變數可以當作<code class=\"language-text\">賦予某個值一個名稱</code>，至於為什麼要命名變數，因為方便我們之後可以直接拿這個變數名稱來使用。</p>\n<p>打開變數區塊=>點擊新增，會看到 tag manager 會預設好幾個比較常用到的變數，click text、url、pathName 等等，下方還可以讓你新增使用者自己的變數，有很多種可以新增，比較常用的會是 dataLayer 帶變數、還有 javascript function return。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>javascript function return - 回傳留言欄位的內容</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'commentValue'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/81f91d5f0d686e3e4ea111acf934dde3/acfc1/tagtitle.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 44.242424242424235%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/81f91d5f0d686e3e4ea111acf934dde3/a805d/tagtitle.webp 495w,\n/static/81f91d5f0d686e3e4ea111acf934dde3/6ec60/tagtitle.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/81f91d5f0d686e3e4ea111acf934dde3/b3db0/tagtitle.png 495w,\n/static/81f91d5f0d686e3e4ea111acf934dde3/acfc1/tagtitle.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/81f91d5f0d686e3e4ea111acf934dde3/acfc1/tagtitle.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager tagtitle\"\n            title=\"tag manager tagtitle\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager tagtitle</figcaption>\n  </figure>\n上面的名稱我取作 comment_value，也就是說之後只要其他地方輸入 {{comment_value}} 就可以取得留言的內容。</p>\n<p>這邊如果不會寫 javascript 的話，也可以使用內建好的變數，記得要勾選後才能被取用。</p>\n<h2 id=\"iii代碼\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#iii%E4%BB%A3%E7%A2%BC\" aria-label=\"iii代碼 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>III.代碼</h2>\n<p>這部分就是 tag manager 的核心，經由設定觸發條件，然後執行代碼。tag manager 整合非常多的不同工具，除了 facebook pixel…。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://support.google.com/tagmanager/answer/6106924\" title=\"tag manager 支援代碼\">tag manager 支援代碼</a></p>\n<p>我們以 ga 設定事件為例子，原本你在 ga 設定事件，會需要在網站上寫<code class=\"language-text\">ga('send', 'event', 類別, 動作, 標籤 )</code>，在這邊都視覺化了，每個類別、動作、標籤都分欄位讓你輸入，所以不用會寫 javascript，你也可以輕易設定事件，更重要是不需要透過工程師幫你處理。</p>\n<p>簡單講就是，你在 tag manager 的追蹤設定，不會影響到原本網站上的程式架構。網站上一定會埋一堆哩哩摳摳的程式碼，對工程師來說每建立一個新頁面都要用整包，畫面不乾淨也不好維運。它可以幫助你追蹤碼分離掉。</p>\n<p>點擊代碼新增 => 選擇 google analytics，使用 ga 的事件。</p>\n<p>再來建立類別、動作、標籤，標籤這邊用我們建立的變數<code class=\"language-text\">comment_value</code>，最後觸發條件再選擇送出留言。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4f91917955ab167117a1271ef0a740d6/acfc1/tagsmaple5.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.96969696969697%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/4f91917955ab167117a1271ef0a740d6/a805d/tagsmaple5.webp 495w,\n/static/4f91917955ab167117a1271ef0a740d6/6ec60/tagsmaple5.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/4f91917955ab167117a1271ef0a740d6/b3db0/tagsmaple5.png 495w,\n/static/4f91917955ab167117a1271ef0a740d6/acfc1/tagsmaple5.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/4f91917955ab167117a1271ef0a740d6/acfc1/tagsmaple5.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager tagsmaple5\"\n            title=\"tag manager tagsmaple5\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager tagsmaple5</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"追蹤-adblock-實作範例\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E8%BF%BD%E8%B9%A4-adblock-%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E7%AF%84%E4%BE%8B\" aria-label=\"追蹤 adblock 實作範例 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>追蹤 adblock 實作範例</h2>\n<p>上面講了一遍後，再來試著操作一遍，需求是，要追蹤來我的 blog 的人，有多少人使用 adblock，使用 ga 事件來記錄。</p>\n<p>以需求來看，觸發點就會是載入頁面後，判斷廣告區塊沒有正常顯示，所以我們要建立一個觸發，執行 ga 事件的代碼。</p>\n<p>這邊來用 tag manager 代碼區塊的自訂 html。建立一個 javascript，這段是要判斷 google-auto-placed 有沒有在 html 上，這是 google 自動廣告會帶的 className，如果沒有這個 class，就代表使用者有裝設 adblock。然後使用<code class=\"language-text\">dataLayer.push({event: 'getAdblock'})</code>產生自訂事件。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>代碼區塊使用自訂 html</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementsByClassName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'google-auto-placed'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    dataLayer<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token literal-property property\">event</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'getAdblock'</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>script<span class=\"token operator\">></span></code></pre></div>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/105c2d39bcfd4c1da74dc900fd577b09/acfc1/tagsample.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.76767676767677%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/105c2d39bcfd4c1da74dc900fd577b09/a805d/tagsample.webp 495w,\n/static/105c2d39bcfd4c1da74dc900fd577b09/6ec60/tagsample.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/105c2d39bcfd4c1da74dc900fd577b09/b3db0/tagsample.png 495w,\n/static/105c2d39bcfd4c1da74dc900fd577b09/acfc1/tagsample.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/105c2d39bcfd4c1da74dc900fd577b09/acfc1/tagsample.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager tagsample\"\n            title=\"tag manager tagsample\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager tagsample</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>接下來，到觸發區塊點選點選 自訂事件，在輸入剛剛 push event 的名稱 getAdblock。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6628bfb6e0e94bbb0eae11d7fe37aadf/acfc1/tagsample3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 42.62626262626262%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/6628bfb6e0e94bbb0eae11d7fe37aadf/a805d/tagsample3.webp 495w,\n/static/6628bfb6e0e94bbb0eae11d7fe37aadf/6ec60/tagsample3.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/6628bfb6e0e94bbb0eae11d7fe37aadf/b3db0/tagsample3.png 495w,\n/static/6628bfb6e0e94bbb0eae11d7fe37aadf/acfc1/tagsample3.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/6628bfb6e0e94bbb0eae11d7fe37aadf/acfc1/tagsample3.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager tagsample3\"\n            title=\"tag manager tagsample3\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager tagsample3</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>進入代碼區塊，建立一個 ga 事件，再輸入事件類別、動作、標籤，觸發就選擇剛剛建好的觸發條件。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"margin: 2vw 0;\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/335ccdfe1ba617cfc95d259a5ae3a336/acfc1/tagsample2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.96969696969697%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/335ccdfe1ba617cfc95d259a5ae3a336/a805d/tagsample2.webp 495w,\n/static/335ccdfe1ba617cfc95d259a5ae3a336/6ec60/tagsample2.webp 800w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/335ccdfe1ba617cfc95d259a5ae3a336/b3db0/tagsample2.png 495w,\n/static/335ccdfe1ba617cfc95d259a5ae3a336/acfc1/tagsample2.png 800w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/335ccdfe1ba617cfc95d259a5ae3a336/acfc1/tagsample2.png\"\n            alt=\"tag manager tagsample2\"\n            title=\"tag manager tagsample2\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">tag manager tagsample2</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p>這樣就大功告成了!!</p>\n<p>ps.記得點開 tag manager 預覽模式，來看一下代碼有沒有成功跑起來。</p>\n<h2 id=\"工作實作心得\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%AF%A6%E4%BD%9C%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97\" aria-label=\"工作實作心得 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>工作實作心得</h2>\n<p>記得我兩年前第一次接觸 tag manager，評語是 <em>這鬼東西太複雜難用了吧</em> 。但不知道是不是兩年間有改版，最近回頭接觸的感想，發現其實滿好用的！特別是預覽模式，很清楚的在發布前測試有沒有設定正確。</p>\n<p>會一直介紹 tag manager 的原因，絕對不是因為我最近每天工作都要接觸 tag manager(眼神死…)，是 tag manager 功能真的太強大了，對前端開發來說也減少非常多的工時，省去在專案上處理各種 ga(xxx)的麻煩、突兀，轉而關注處理 dataLayer。</p>\n<p>最後最後，如果你是行銷人，然後會用 tag manager 的話，我非常敬佩你。</p>\n<p>感謝閱讀！</p>\n<!--- ![google tagmanager](../images/tagtool.png \"google tagmanager\") --->\n","fields":{"readingTime":{"text":"11 min read"}},"frontmatter":{"title":"Google Tag Manager(gtm)教學 觸發、代碼、變數設定介紹","date":"October 16, 2018","description":"完整介紹tag manager功能設定細節、功能，建立流程步驟教學，以留言板追蹤為範例。假設我們要追蹤送出留言，建立一個事件，拿進ga當作轉換目標。","categories":"marketing","tags":["tag_manager","google_analytics"],